Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Depends: libc6 (>= 2.31), libnotify-bin, libice6, libsm6, libx11-6, libxft2, libxext6, libssl3
Maintainer: Abiruzzaman Molla <abiruzzaman@example.com>
Description: Daily Prayer Timer - Cross-Platform
 A high-performance desktop application for accurate prayer times,
 Qibla direction, digital tasbih, dua library, Ramadan tracker,
 and deed tracking. Built with Avalonia UI for Linux.
